Package org.firstinspires.ftc.ftccommon.internal

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FtcRobotControllerWatchdogService
    FtcRobotControllerWatchdogService is a simple sticky service that we use to detect a crash of the robot controller process and auto-restart the robot controller activity when that happens.
    FtcRobotControllerWatchdogService.ActivityFinder  
    ProgramAndManageActivity
    This is a dummy class, used in the OpenFTC Turbo build variant
    RunOnBoot
    RunOnBoot is responsible for auto-starting the robot controller app when a headless device boots.
